---
title: Double Herby-Honey Halloumi & Veggie Couscous with Almonds & Yoghurt
description: Whip up a halloumi and couscous extravaganza in four easy steps. Drizzle over some honey to coat the halloumi and toss the
couscous with some carrot and courgette - it will look and taste like you’ve been cooking for hours!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6789c25ef50643e26c99899d-c5cfbe34.jpeg
